This edition
------------
This edition adds YOLO26 model weights, which are AGPL-3.0-covered. The combined
work distributed from this repository is therefore licensed under AGPL-3.0 (see
LICENSE). Distributing a build from here carries AGPL-3.0 obligations, including
providing complete corresponding source for that build.

Model weights carry their own licenses and training dataset terms, independent of
any code license. The bundled semantic segmentation model is trained on
Cityscapes, which is restricted to NON-COMMERCIAL use. See docs/yolo-models.md
for full provenance of both models.

Not affiliated with, endorsed by, or sponsored by Ultralytics. "YOLO" is used
descriptively to identify the models this edition integrates.

